events_found.title: Acupuncture & Sound Healing Sanctuary
events_found.description: An inviting and supportive afternoon offering guided self-massage, acupuncture, and sound healing in community. Come join us at a private home in Sunnyvale for a rejuvenating day of self-massage, community acupuncture, and sound healing. Together, well honor the letting-go energy of fall and prepare for the winter season  embodying receptivity, retrospection, and the invitation to go deep. In addition to guided experiences, youll have time for journaling, quiet connection, and moments of nourishment and rest at your own pace. Youll be supported by a team of gifted healers, each sharing their unique expertise to help you soften, restore, and reset.
